                </p>
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    <div class="testimonial-avatar me-3">
                        <i class="fas fa-user fa-2x text-primary"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold mb-0">Marcus Thompson</h5>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-0">Owner, Soul Food Kitchen</p>
                        <small class="text-muted">Atlanta, GA</small>
